It didn’t matter that our online presence would turn out to be far larger than our typical Sunday gatherings.
I didn’t ache for online presence; I ached for actual presence, the communion of the saints, the body of Christ.
Our First LivestreamMark Carlsson, senior pastor at Good Shepherd Church in Naperville, Illinois:Good Shepherd Church hosted our first-ever online worship service last weekend.
Online services have been requested for some time, and the current global crisis expedited the introduction and execution of it.
We also moved our church counseling services online so people can still meet one on one with a peer counselor.